{{!--
Timed-effect reminder card. Posted by the event queue when a scheduled effect
comes DUE — it never performs the effect. The [Perform] button is an
`action-card-button` addressed to the effect's document (data-handler-uuid), so the
character's owner runs the deferred action on their click (the same executor the
queue used to run automatically). Owner-gated at render time
(gateActionCardButtons) and re-authorized at click (issue #167).
--}}
<div class="hmk chat-card item-card">
    <header class="card-header">
        <h3 class="title">{{effectLabel}}</h3>
        <h4 class="subtitle">{{actorName}}</h4>
    </header>

    <div class="card-content center">
        <span>{{body}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card-buttons">
        <button
            class="action-card-button"
            data-action="{{actionName}}"
            data-handler-uuid="{{handlerUuid}}"
            data-scope="{{toJSON scopeData}}"
        >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-hourglass-half"></i> {{performLabel}}
        </button>
    </div>
</div>
